# MAGI API Configuration
# Copy this file to key.env and fill in any keys you want available in dev mode.
# key.env is gitignored and will NOT be committed or bundled into release builds.
#
# These same keys can also be entered in Settings → AI Provider inside the app.
# Released builds NEVER bundle keys — every user supplies their own.

